## Relation to other rules

- **000-project-bootstrap.mdc**: Orchestration flow (Planner → software-architect → Implementer → Tester → Verifier, with variants per workflow). Use Task tool to invoke these roles; they update handoff in the workspace.
- **100-token-economics.mdc**: Delegation reduces main context. When context grows, delegate rather than loading more files. Pass Engram references (~50 tokens) instead of full content (3,000–15,000 tokens).
- **300-engram-memory.mdc**: Subagents should `mem_save` significant work before returning. Orchestrator passes relevant `mem_context` in subagent prompts.
- **Handoff**: Subagents update the handoff file (path from `handoff_file`; per-workflow to avoid parallel bottleneck). Main agent reads handoff to continue or hand off to the next role.
